{"tid":1430784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國提升對香港旅遊警示至第二級別　指香港出現內亂","createTime":"2019-08-07T23:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:39:00.000Z","uid":20933,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5f63c12ba5577c1c4c36e26d74491c7760fb2d","tid":1430784,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1473360_2_20190808054147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1473360_2_20190808054147.jpg&h=5f583481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院宣布，提升對香港旅遊警示至第二級別。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊警示的內容說明，由於香港出現內亂（civil unrest），呼籲美國公民在香港境內活動時需要更加謹慎。<br />\n<br />\n警示表示，香港自從六月以來，在不同區域先後舉行多次大規模及較小規模的政治示威活動，雖然大多數都是和平舉行，但部分出現激烈對抗或演變成暴力衝突，這類示威活動，在短時間內或未有事先公布的情況下舉行，情況可能持續。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊警示呼籲在港的美國公民，要密切留意本地的最新新聞資訊、避免前往示威區域、身處示威地點附近要謹慎行事，注意週圍環境及保持低調。"},{"pid":"e560cfeb5805d11fd4375ed04ef447fc5d86fc0b","tid":1430784,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:32:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473360-20190808.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473360-20190808.htm&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=e63a8282\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473360-20190808.htm&h=80d03ed1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473360-20190808.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b64c820c1639295cd03c3f483f0f615072ad94a8","tid":1430784,"uid":222190,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5i1ogox.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5i1ogox.png&h=0dc48565&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1kcF23x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3